with adults or other children,they are first and foremost victims of child sexual abuse. |access-date=2015-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150912142724/https://www.ncjtc.org/NCJTC_Member_Resources/Public/Child%20Pornography%20Criminal%20Justice%20Response.pdf |archive-date=2015-09-12 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="Wortley17">{{cite journal|title=Child Pornography on the Internet |first=Richard |last=Wortley |author2=Stephen Smallbone |journal=Problem-Oriented Guides for Police |volume=No. 41|page=17|quote=The children portrayed in child pornography are first victimized when their abuse is perpetrated and recorded. They are further victimized each time that record is accessed.}}</ref><ref name="sheldon9">{{cite book|title=Sex Offenders and the Internet |url=https://archive.org/details/sexoffendersinte00howi |first=Kerry |last=Sheldon |author2=Dennis Howitt |page=[https://archive.org/details/sexoffendersinte00howi/page/9 9] |publisher=John Wiley and Sons |year=2007|isbn=0-470-02800-9|quote=...supplying the material to meet this demand results in the further abuse of children  Pictures, films and videos function as a permanent record of the original sexual abuse. Consequently, memories of the trauma and abuse are maintained as long as the record exists.  Victims filmed and photographed many years ago will nevertheless be aware throughout their lifetimes that their childhood victimization continues to be exploited perversely.}}</ref><ref name="UNESCO1999" /> 儿童色情会通过各種媒介进行传播，<ref name="missingkids">{{cite web|url=http://www.missingkids.com/missingkids/servlet/PageServlet?LanguageCountry=en_US&PageId=1504|title=What is Child Pornography|accessdate=2008-04-30|work=NCMEC|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080508024202/http://www.missingkids.com/missingkids/servlet/PageServlet?LanguageCountry=en_US&PageId=1504|archivedate=2008-05-08}}</ref> 这包括[[情色文學|文章]]<ref name="Akdeniz11" /><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.efc.ca/pages/law/cc/cc.163.1.html |title=Definition of 'Child Pornography' |work=Criminal Code of Canada, Section 163.1 |publisher=Electronic Frontier Canada |year=2004 |access-date=2009-03-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090302020551/http://efc.ca/pages/law/cc/cc.163.1.html |archive-date=2009-03-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/canada/story/2002/03/26/sharpe020326.html |title=Sharpe Not Guilty of Possessing Written Child Pornography |publisher=CBC News |date=2002-03-26 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080508232255/http://www.cbc.ca/canada/story/2002/03/26/sharpe020326.html |archivedate=2008-05-08 |accessdate=2018-06-11 }}</ref>、[[杂志|杂志]]、[[照片|照片]]<ref name="missingkids" />、[[雕塑|雕塑]]<ref name="missingkids" />、[[素描|素描]]<ref name="missingkids" />、[[绘画|绘画]]<ref name="missingkids" />、[[动画|动画]]<ref name="missingkids" />、[[录音|录音]]<ref name="AkdenizX">{{cite book|title=Internet child pornography and the law: national and international responses |url=https://archive.org/details/internetchildpor00akde_982 |first=Yaman |last=Akdeniz| publisher=Ashgate Publishing, Ltd. |year=2008|page=[https://archive.org/details/internetchildpor00akde_982/page/n171 153]|isbn=0-7546-2297-5}}</ref>、[[色情片|电影]]、[[视频|视频]]<ref name="missingkids" />及[[电子游戏|电子游戏]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://digiknow.ninemsn.com/gaming/gamesfeatures/8255964/child-porn-video-game-rated-pg-in-australia |title="Child Porn" video game rated PG in Australia |work=digiknow |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203005858/http://digiknow.ninemsn.com/gaming/gamesfeatures/8255964/child-porn-video-game-rated-pg-in-australia |archivedate=2013-12-03 |accessdate=2018-06-11 }}</ref>等。

[[儿童色情制品的合法性|关于儿童色情制品的法律]]通常涵蓋處於[[前青少年期|前青少年期]]、[[青春期|青春期]]及后青少年期的人的性相关图像，以及利用电脑制图手段生成的相关内容作品。<ref name=doj1/> 大多数被逮捕的儿童色情制品持有者都被發現持有[[前青少年期|前青少年期]]的儿童色情制品；而持有后青少年期[[青少年|青少年]]儿童色情制品的人士则有很大可能不会被逮捕，即便这些图像也属于法律规管的范围。<ref name=doj1/>

儿童色情制品的生产者正试图通过跨国分发其制品来规避法律诉讼，尽管过去几年来通过定期逮捕一些国家的嫌疑人正越来越多地解决这个问题。<ref name=doj1/><ref name=ncmec/> 涉及前青少年期的儿童色情制品多由[[恋童|恋童者]]基于多种理由观看或搜集，例如：私人性目的（[[自慰|自慰]]等）、与其他恋童者交易、筹备进行儿童性虐待（[[儿童性诱拐|儿童性诱拐]]）、诱惑导致诱捕性[[性剥削|性剥削]]（制作新的儿童色情制品或[[雛妓|儿童性交易]]）等。<ref name=CrossonTower208>{{cite book|title=Understanding child abuse and neglect  |url=https://archive.org/details/understandingchi0000cros  |first=Cynthia |last=Crosson-Tower |isbn=0-205-40183-X |publisher=Allyn & Bacon |year=2005|page=[https://archive.org/details/understandingchi0000cros/page/208 208]}}</ref><ref name=Wortley14>{{cite journal|title=Child Pornography on the Internet |author1=Richard Wortley |author2=Stephen Smallbone |journal=Problem-Oriented Guides for Police |volume=No. 41|pages=14–16}}</ref><ref name= Levesque64>{{cite book |title=Sexual Abuse of Children: A Human Rights Perspective |url=https://archive.org/details/sexualabuseofchi0000leve |first=Roger J. R. |last=Levesque |year=1999 |page=[https://archive.org/details/sexualabuseofchi0000leve/page/64 64]|publisher=Indiana University |isbn= 0-253-33471-3}}</ref> 参与儿童色情制品制作的儿童有的是自願主动參與的，有的則遭成年人[[约制|胁迫]]參與。<ref>{{cite web |quote=Children and young people take photos and videos themselves either voluntarily or as a result of bullying or manipulation by a sexual predator, often channelled through a webcam. |title=End Child Pornography |url=http://www.ecpat.net/end-child-pornography |author=ECPAT |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150102051435/http://www.ecpat.net/end-child-pornography |archivedate=2015-01-02 |accessdate=2018-06-11 }}</ref>

儿童色情制品在全球绝大多数的司法管辖区都是非法并受到[[审查制度|审查]]的。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.missingkids.com/en_US/documents/CP_Legislation_Report.pdf |title=存档副本 |access-date=2012-08-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121120173350/http://www.missingkids.com/en_US/documents/CP_Legislation_Report.pdf |archive-date=2012-11-20 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.csecworldcongress.org/en/index.htm |title=World Congress against CSEC |publisher=Csecworldcongress.org |date=2002-07-27 |accessdate=2012-01-07 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120316121435/http://www.csecworldcongress.org/en/index.htm |archivedate=2012-03-16 }}</ref> 截至2008年，[[国际刑警组织|国际刑警组织]]的187个成员国或地区中有94个制订了针对儿童色情制品的法律，这还不包括那些完全禁止任何色情制品的国家或地区。<ref name=icmec/> 在这94个制订专门法的国家或地区里，有58个国家或地区直接将持有儿童色情制品定为违法，而不考虑其是否分发这些制品。<ref name=icmec/> 在几乎所有的西方国家里，分发或持有儿童色情制品都是刑事犯罪。一项广泛的运动旨在推动儿童色情制品刑事定罪全球化，这项运动的推动者包括[[联合国|联合国]]和[[欧洲联盟委员会|欧盟委员会]]。<ref name= Akdeniz11/><ref name=worldcongress>{{cite web |url=http://www.csecworldcongress.org/en/index.htm |title=World Congress against Commercial Sexual Exploitation of Children |publisher= |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120316121435/http://www.csecworldcongress.org/en/index.htm |archivedate=2012-03-16 |accessdate=2018-07-28 }}</ref>

