进入21世纪之后，执法人员与学者更多地使用“'''儿童虐待图像'''（{{lang|en|Child Abuse Images}}）”这个术语，因为“色情制品”这个属于可能含有同意这样的不准确含义以及与材料的虐待性质产生距离等问题。<ref name= Akdeniz11/><ref name="Wortley"/><ref name="Sanderson"/><ref name=interpolTerm>{{cite web |title=Blocking access to child abuse material – Terminology |url=http://www.interpol.int/Public/THBInternetAccessBlocking/Terminology.asp |publisher=INTERPOL |accessdate=2018-07-28 |archive-date=2010-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101008114025/http://www.interpol.int/Public/THBInternetAccessBlocking/Terminology.asp |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name=nspccCAI>{{cite web |url=http://www.nspcc.org.uk/Inform/policyandpublicaffairs/policysummaries/childabuseimages_wdf56933.pdf |title=NSPCC Policy Summary – Child Abuse Images |date=2008-04 |publisher=National Society for the Prevention of Cruelty to Children, London, UK |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110626051703/http://www.nspcc.org.uk/Inform/policyandpublicaffairs/policysummaries/childabuseimages_wdf56933.pdf |archivedate=2011-06-26 |accessdate=2018-07-28 }}</ref> 一个相似的术语，“'''儿童性虐待材料'''（{{lang|en|Child Sexual Abuse Material}}）”被一些官方机构所采用。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.acorn.gov.au/what-is-cybercrime/online-child-sexual-abuse-material/|title=Online child sexual abuse material|first=|last=admin|date=2015-12-23|publisher=|access-date=2016-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160421071437/http://www.acorn.gov.au/what-is-cybercrime/online-child-sexual-abuse-material/|archive-date=2016-04-21|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.interpol.int/Crime-areas/Crimes-against-children/Access-blocking|title=Access blocking / Crimes against children / Crime areas / Internet / Home - INTERPOL|publisher=|accessdate=2016-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161221084326/https://www.interpol.int/Crime-areas/Crimes-against-children/Access-blocking|archive-date=2016-12-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.europol.europa.eu/content/industry-reporting-child-sexual-abuse-material |title=Industry Reporting of Child Sexual Abuse Material - Europol |publisher= |accessdate=2016-09-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160817032415/https://www.europol.europa.eu/content/industry-reporting-child-sexual-abuse-material |archivedate=2016-08-17 }}</ref> 此外还有一些相似的术语也在被使用，比如：“儿童虐待材料（{{lang|en|Child Abuse Material}}）”、“儿童性虐待记录（{{lang|en|Documented Child Sexual Abuse}}）”、“儿童性虐待描述（{{lang|en|Depicted Child Sexual Abuse}}）”；同时，西方国家也会使用“{{lang|en|CAI}}”或“{{lang|en|CAM}}”作为对应的缩写。<ref name=interpolTerm/> 各司法管辖区对于术语“儿童色情”的法律定义都是各自保留的，与之相关的术语还有“儿童不雅照”等。<ref name= Akdeniz11/><ref name= Wortley/><ref name= Sanderson/><ref name=copine>{{cite journal|title=The COPINE Project |first= Ethel |last= Quayle |issn=1649-6396 <!-- Note that the journal itself lists 1649-639X, an invalid ISSN -->  |volume= 5 |date=September 2008 |journal=Irish Probation Journal |publisher=Probation Board for Northern Ireland}}</ref> 2008年，反对儿童及青少年性剥削第三次世界大会（{{lang|en|World Congress III against the Sexual Exploitation of Children and Adolescents}}）在其正式-{zh-tw:通過;zh-cn:通过;}-的协议里指出，“‘儿童虐待图像’越来越多被用来指代色情制品中的儿童与青少年性剥削。这是为了反映这种现象的严重性，以及强调儿童色情图像实际上就是犯罪记录。”<ref name=Mathew>{{cite journal |last=Mathew |first=Lina A. |title=Online Child Safety from Sexual Abuse in India |volume=2009 |journal=Journal of Information, Law & Technology |url=http://go.warwick.ac.uk/jilt/2009_1/mathew |page=21 |issue=1 |access-date=2018-07-28 |archive-date=2020-05-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200521164546/http://go.warwick.ac.uk/jilt/2009_1/mathew/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

[[国际刑警组织|国际刑警组织]]及各国警务机构（包括[[美国司法部|美国司法部]]）都在执行国际上通行的儿童色情法。自1999年以来，国际刑警组织关于针对未成年犯罪的常设工作小组使用了如下定义：
{{quote|儿童色情是针对儿童性虐待或性剥削的结果。它可以被定义为任何描绘或促使针对儿童性虐待的方式，这包括以儿童性器官或儿童性行为为内容重点的文字、图像及音频等。<ref name=UNESCO1999>{{cite web |url=http://unesdoc.unesco.org/images/0011/001147/114734eo.pdf |format=PDF |title=Sexual Abuse of Children on the Internet: A New Challenge for INTERPOL |author=Agnes Fournier de Saint Maur |date=1999-01 |publisher=[[UNESCO|UNESCO]] (United Nations Educational, Scientific and Cultural Organization) |work=Expert Meeting on Sexual Abuse of Children, Child Pornography and Paedophilia on the Internet: an international challenge |access-date=2010-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110408205629/http://unesdoc.unesco.org/images/0011/001147/114734eo.pdf |archive-date=2011-04-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref>}}

== 儿童性虐待的生产与分发 ==
所有年龄段的儿童，甚至包括[[婴儿|婴儿]]，<ref name=Infants>{{cite news |url=https://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=990DE3DA1330F93AA25754C0A96E958260&scp=1&sq=dutch+sex+ring&st=nyt
|title=Dutch Say A Sex Ring Used Infants On Internet|accessdate=2008-05-01 |work=New York Times | first=Marlise | last=Simons | date=1998-07-19}}</ref> 都在色情作品的制作中遭遇过虐待。<ref name=sheldon20/><ref name=doj1/> [[美国司法部|美国司法部]]的估计，仅仅是色情业者手中就记录了超过100万次的美国儿童性虐待行为。<ref name= Levesque>{{cite book|title=Sexual Abuse of Children: A Human Rights Perspective|url=https://archive.org/details/sexualabuseofchi0000leve|first=Roger J.R. |last=Levesque |year=1999 |publisher=Indiana University Press |page=[https://archive.org/details/sexualabuseofchi0000leve/page/66 66]|isbn=0-253-33471-3}}</ref> 而实际上可能有更多的年幼受害者和更残忍的行为在发生，美国联邦{{Link-en|网络儿童犯罪小组|Internet Crimes Against Children}}探员弗林特·沃特斯（{{lang|en|Flint Waters}}）的说道，“这些家伙正在强奸婴儿和幼童。你可以在那些视频里听到孩子们的哭泣和哀求。这是非常可怕的。”<ref>{{cite web|title=The Child Porn Pipeline Part Three: A child victim's story of betrayal and despair|url=http://www.buffalonews.com/339/story/184849.html|year=2008|work=Buffalo News|access-date=2008-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090722011623/http://www.buffalonews.com/339/story/184849.html|archive-date=2009-07-22|dead-url=no}}</ref> 而根据“反对对儿童进行商业性剥削世界大会（{{lang|en|World Congress against Commercial Sexual Exploitation of Children}}）”的说法，“虽然不可能获得准确的数据，但是国际市场上可以轻易获得儿童色情制品，这表明有越来越多的儿童通过这一媒介被进行性剥削。”<ref name="healty">{{cite web |url=http://www.csecworldcongress.org/PDF/en/Stockholm/Background_reading/Theme_papers/Theme%20paper%20Pornography%201996_EN.pdf |title=Child pornography: an international perspective'', Margaret A. Healty, 1996 |publisher= |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080228232548/http://www.csecworldcongress.org/PDF/en/Stockholm/Background_reading/Theme_papers/Theme%20paper%20Pornography%201996_EN.pdf |archivedate=2008-02-28 |accessdate=2018-07-28 }}</ref> [[英国|英国]]儿童福利组织{{Link-en|为了孩子行动|Action for Children|全国儿童之家}}表示，由于互联网上对于儿童色情制品的需求不断增加，这导致了儿童遭受性虐待案件的增加，从而也增加了在儿童色情制品生产过程中儿童受害者数量的增加。<ref name="gu20040112">{{cite news | title = Internet porn 'increasing child abuse' | url = https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2004/jan/12/childprotection.childrensservices | work = Guardian Unlimited | publisher = Guardian News and Media Limited | date = 2004-01-12 | accessdate = 2007-06-01 | location = London | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140912210957/http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2004/jan/12/childprotection.childrensservices | archive-date = 2014-09-12 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

